title Space-Based Telecoms Landscape (Feb 2023)
style wardley

// Anchors — three user classes with different needs
anchor Consumer [0.98, 0.70]
anchor Corporation [0.96, 0.60]
anchor Government [0.94, 0.45]

// User-visible services (what the anchors actually consume)
component Rural / Remote Broadband [0.88, 0.55]
component Mobile Connectivity (voice + data) [0.87, 0.85]
component In-Flight / Maritime Connectivity [0.85, 0.50]
component Enterprise WAN / Backhaul [0.84, 0.70]
