component Network Access [0.76, 0.80]
component Terrestrial Mobile (4G/5G) [0.70, 0.88]
component Fibre / Fixed Line [0.68, 0.95]
component Non-Terrestrial Network (NTN, 3GPP Rel-17) [0.66, 0.28]
component Satellite Direct-to-Cell (T-Mo/SpaceX, AST, Lynk) [0.64, 0.10]
component Terrestrial Broadcast Tower [0.72, 0.94]

// Topology & physical network substrate
component Physical Network Topology [0.62, 0.70]
component Ground-to-Satellite Link [0.58, 0.55]

